{"tid":2173040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"電腦技術員涉去年10月九龍區衝突 事隔10個月後正式起訴暴動等罪 羅德泉拒絕被告保釋","createTime":"2020-08-25T04:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T05:25:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"875f752cdd1ce340c75e430789a368a37429164c","tid":2173040,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"去年 10 月 27 日，網民於尖沙咀發起「追究警暴」集會，最終演變成九龍區多處警民衝突。32 歲電腦技術員被指在長沙灣政府合署外攜有汽油彈，去年 12 月「踢保」後，昨天再度被捕。被告被控暴動、使用蒙面物品等 3 罪，今（25 日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂。裁判官拒絕被告保釋，押至 10 月 6 日再訊，期間還押懲教看管。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89-10-27-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%93%A1-%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D-%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%AD%89-3-%E7%BD%AA-%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E8%87%B3-10-%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589-10-27-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25AD%2589-3-%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3-10-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=3b3ed0f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589-10-27-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D-%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25AD%2589-3-%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E8%2587%25B3-10-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=d76be225\" dat