:11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"又係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71142ec4edaae12d5e77805c358848c65063ec3","tid":2173040,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"800180e8962c0d654554eb0c999e634a085b306c","tid":2173040,"uid":63400,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"做得暴徒，一係收咗錢，一係傻西，甘心為政治明星墊屍底。又唔見連登冷氣軍師畀人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，早啲拉晒坐監都係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"牙國泉就真係收左錢啦傻閪"},{"pid":"5bbe434a212da4f6566733f5b5345f0e90d56e38","tid":2173040,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/2JBIDHOCTNAWDBGU5PJA6B5KWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2F2JBIDHOCTNAWDBGU5PJA6B5KWA%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=4f20eb3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2F2JBIDHOCTNAWDBGU5PJA6B5KWA%2F&h=3a86cf65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/2JBIDHOCTNAWDBGU5PJA6B5KWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10月27日市民於尖沙嘴舉行「追究警暴」集會，其間演變成警民衝突。當日有近70名示威者於長沙灣政府合署外聚集，其間有電腦技術維修員在其他示威者撐傘掩護下，涉以汽油彈掟向政府合署的閘口。警方到場驅散並將維修員拘捕，並在其背囊找到載有易燃液體的玻璃樽及火槍。維修員一度「踢保」，日前再被捕，被控暴動等三罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院提訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方今指需時等候轉介文件，案件將在區域法院審理，被告申請保釋，但被主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕。案件押後至10月6日再訊，以待控方準備轉介文件，其間被告須還柙監房候訊。"}]}